  "text": "Our goal is now to justify these claims by standard worldsheet methods. The (2, 1) string theory is strictly speaking outside the range of the definition given at the beginning of section 1.2, since the Kac table is empty and there is no (2, 1) minimal model. A possible definition is formal analytic continuation to k → 0 of the double-scaling results [CITATION_1] , but this is unsatisfactory for our purposes. Fortunately, there are several other more intrinsic formulations, appearing to all yield the same results.",
